 response‚Üêrequest Handle_GET_REST_Version1 path_;packageID;json;path;data;html;regFolder;specialCommands;groupName
‚çù Handles all commands defined in version 1 of the REST interface
 path_‚Üì‚ç®‚Üê-'/'=¬Ø1‚Üëpath_
 :If 1='/'+.=path_
     path‚Üêpath_
     packageID‚Üê''
 :Else
     (path packageID)‚ÜêReg.SeparateUriAndPackageID path_
     path‚Üì‚ç®‚Üê-'/'=¬Ø1‚Üëpath
 :EndIf
 path‚Üê‚éïC path
 specialCommands‚ÜêGetSpecialCommands request.Method
 :If (‚äÇpath)‚àä(‚äÇ'v1/'),¬®specialCommands
     response‚Üêrequest ProcessTestCommands ‚éïC path
 :Else
     :If path‚â°GetVersion_REST'groups'
     :AndIf 0<‚â¢packageID
     :AndIf 0=Reg.IsValidPackageID_Complete packageID
          ‚çù Special case: somebody asked for the home page of a group via a browser
         :If G.INI.Exist'CONFIG:GroupHomePages'
         :AndIf G.INI.Get'CONFIG:GroupHomePages'
             groupName‚Üê1‚Üì{‚çµ‚Üë‚ç®-‚åä/'/\'‚ç≥‚ç®‚åΩ‚çµ}path_
             response‚ÜêReturnGroupHomepage packageID request
         :Else
             response‚Üêrequest RespondWithHTML 404
         :EndIf
     :Else
         :Select path
         :Case GetVersion_REST'all_packages'                ‚çù Inactive since 0.79.0, and a candiate for being removed alltogether
             response‚Üêrequest GetFullPackageList packageID
         :Case GetVersion_REST'copy-registry'
             response‚Üêrequest GetFullPackageList''
         :Case GetVersion_REST'packages'
             response‚Üêrequest GetPackageList packageID
         :Case GetVersion_REST'deprecated-pkgs'
             response‚ÜêGetDeprecatedPackages request
         :Case GetVersion_REST'packages/major_versions'
             regFolder‚Üê'expand'F.NormalizePath G.RegistryPath
             response‚Üêrequest GetMajorVersionList packageID regFolder
         :Case GetVersion_REST'packages/versions'
             response‚Üêrequest GetVersionList packageID
         :Case GetVersion_REST'packages/details'
             response‚Üêrequest GetDetails packageID
         :Case GetVersion_REST'packages/dependencies'
             response‚Üêrequest ReturnDependencyFiles packageID
         :Case GetVersion_REST'packages/exist'
             response‚Üêrequest CheckForExistence packageID
         :Case GetVersion_REST'packages/dependencies'
             response‚Üêrequest GetDependencies packageID
         :Case GetVersion_REST'packages/best_version'
             response‚Üêrequest GetBestVersionNumber packageID
         :Case GetVersion_REST'groups'
             response‚ÜêGetGroupList ‚ç¨
         :Case GetVersion_REST'tags'
             response‚ÜêGetTagList request
         :Case GetVersion_REST'documentation'
             response‚Üêrequest RedirectTo'https://aplteam.github.io/Tatin/'
         :Case GetVersion_REST'version'
             response‚ÜêGetServerVersion request
         :Case GetVersion_REST'minimum-version'
             response‚ÜêGetMinimumServerVersion request
         :Case GetVersion_REST'version-information'
             response‚ÜêGetVersionInformation request
         :Case GetVersion_REST'delete-policy'
             response‚ÜêReturnDeletePolicy request
         :Case GetVersion_REST'credential-report'
             response‚ÜêReturnCredentialReport request
         :Case GetVersion_REST'usage-data'
             response‚ÜêReturnUsageData request
         :Case GetVersion_REST'group-homepage'
             response‚ÜêHandleGroupHomePage request
         :Case GetVersion_REST'group-homepage-edit'
             response‚ÜêEditGroupHomepage request
         :Case GetVersion_REST'group-homepage-create'
             response‚ÜêEditGroupHomepage request
         :Case GetVersion_REST'get-licenses'
             response‚ÜêReturnLicenses request
         :Case GetVersion_REST'dependencies'
             response‚ÜêReturnDependencies request
         :Else
         ‚çù Something new?
             response‚Üêrequest RespondWithHTML 400 'Invalid Request' ‚çù Not a valid REST version 1 request
         :EndSelect
     :EndIf
 :EndIf
‚çùDone
